    "environment_rating": "dry",
    "family_description": "Edge-lit LED exit sign with 6 inch letters and injection-molded high-impact acrylic panel in clear, mirror, or white background. Red or deep green letter colors; NFPA 101 compliant chevron directional indicators when specified. Recessed variant uses an 18-gauge die-formed steel housing with aluminum trim; surface variant is all aluminum. Extruded trim plate secured by torsion springs with no visible mounting hardware. Dual voltage 120/277 VAC 60 Hz. Self-powered (ES7) models add a sealed maintenance-free nickel cadmium battery (10-year life expectancy, 24-hour max recharge) that illuminates the sign face for 90 minutes during a power interruption; this AC-only (ES6) configuration has no battery. UL 924 Listed, Life Safety NFPA 101, NEC/OSHA.",
